products.title: ecru mug 10 cm - Speckled Sand
products.body_html:
Toxins free, sustainable & eco friendly stoneware.

Dishwasher, microwave & oven safe.

Care & use:

Please use a soft brush and dish soap, and avoid metal and abrasive sponges.

Don't take it out from very hot temperatures to countertops.

Always place it on a heat proof mat when taken out of high temperatures, don't place over cold surfaces (like kitchen countertops) to avoid cracks.

Don't take it out of a refrigerator to a high temperature, leave it in room temperature for a while before placing it in a microwave or oven.
